thread.title: Arren
thread.title_full: Trewarne Fine Jewellery reviewed by Arren

author: Arren
title: Arren
text:
Through a sea of jewelers, Trewarne outshines many. Finding an engagement ring can be a dauntimg task, cuts, clarity and design options are endless.
The staff at Trewarne were informative and attentive, but most importantly they were patient. They showed various designs and styles, painstakingly so, untill i found wjat I wanted at a price to suit.
An great retailer, i recommend anyone to investigate!
